channel.title: iPod commercial I made a couple years ago
channel.description:
[youtube]JEEiXvTDGCQ[/youtube] 3Ds Max model. Don't even ask how many poly's, I way overdid it because it was one of my first projects. I converted the file and shrunk it wrong, and so it's a little out of sync to the music, and there is a piece at the end there that says "completely remastered" which originally lasted about a second, but the compression screwed that up. First and last time I try to use windows movie maker to convert a movie.
I think I still have the high quality version that is synced better, I might upload it at some point.
